### Login to get token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user7.test@example.com",
    "password": "pass1234"
}

### User log out -> clear token
POST http://localhost:3000/api/users/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "user7.test@example.com",
    "password": "pass1234"
}

### Add product to shoping cart (Requires Login)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/carts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "6a1914e63b9010b699421c84",
    "quantity": 1
}

### Get cart details
GET http://localhost:3000/api/carts

### Edit cart item quantity
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/carts
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "6a1914e63b9010b699421c84",
    "quantity": 10
}

### Clear all items from cart
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/carts
